snippet.title: ICEwall Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1835970/ICEwall/

New gameplay trailer for my upcoming roguelite shoot'em up: ICEwall.
If you like what you see, make sure to wishlist on Steam, it helps a lot!

You can play the demo on Steam now!
